\date{2025-03-19}
\title{Conflict detection and ordering datastructures}
\author{cjj39}

\p{
  The primary purpose of most deployed consensus protocols is to order requests.
  Hence the datastructure used is relevant.
}

\p{
  These datastructures can be very simple, from a lock around the value, to the very complex, a DAG of transactions
}
